{"ja363:0.1":"Jataka ","ja363:0.2":"Pancakanipata ","ja363:0.3":"Vannarohavagga ","ja363:0.4":"3. Hirijataka ","ja363:1.1":"“Hirim tarantam vijigucchamanam, ","ja363:1.2":"Tavahamasmi iti bhasamanam; ","ja363:1.3":"Seyyani kammani anadiyantam, ","ja363:1.4":"Neso mamanti iti nam vijanna. ","ja363:2.1":"Yanhi kayira tanhi vade, ","ja363:2.2":"yam na kayira na tam vade; ","ja363:2.3":"Akarontam bhasamanam, ","ja363:2.4":"parijananti pandita. ","ja363:3.1":"Na so mitto yo sada appamatto, ","ja363:3.2":"Bhedasanki randhamevanupassi; ","ja363:3.3":"Yasminca seti urasiva putto, ","ja363:3.4":"Sa ve mitto yo abhejjo parehi. ","ja363:4.1":"Pamojjakaranam thanam, ","ja363:4.2":"pasamsavahanam sukham; ","ja363:4.3":"Phalanisamso bhaveti, ","ja363:4.4":"vahanto porisam dhuram. ","ja363:5.1":"Pavivekarasam pitva, ","ja363:5.2":"rasam upasamassa ca; ","ja363:5.3":"Niddaro hoti nippapo, ","ja363:5.4":"dhammappitirasam pivan”ti. ","ja363:6.1":"Hirijatakam tatiyam. "}